public interface ISaveableWorkbenchPart
extends ISaveablePart, IWorkbenchPart
    Deprecated.
    Clients should use a subclass of CompareEditorInput and CompareUI.openCompareDialog(org.eclipse.compare.CompareEditorInput)
    A saveable workbench part is a visual component that can be shown within different contexts (e.g a dialog, workbench page).
